PR7 training events observation patch
=====================================

This patch is applied by:

  python scripts/third_party/apply_gaussian_splatting_observation_patch.py \
    --third-party-root ./third_party \
    --patch pr7_training_events

The generated patch adds marker-delimited, observation-only hooks to the local
official Gaussian Splatting `train.py` clone.

Markers:

  # VIEWTRUST PR7 OBSERVATION START
  # VIEWTRUST PR7 OBSERVATION END

The patch is intentionally generated by the script instead of committed as a
patched third_party source file. This file documents the patch identity and
server workflow; do not apply it with `patch` directly.

Safety policy:

  - no loss changes
  - no optimizer changes
  - no camera sampling changes
  - no rendering changes
  - no densification threshold or decision changes
  - no pruning or opacity reset decision changes
  - no third_party source is committed to ViewTrust-GS

The observer activates only when:

  VIEWTRUST_ENABLE_TRAINING_EVENTS=1

Otherwise the official trainer should behave as before.
